org.apache.flex.compiler.tree.as

Interface IImportNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IASNode, ISourceLocation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ImportNode, MXMLImplicitImportNode

    public interface IImportNode
extends IASNode
    An AST node representing an import directive.

    The shape of this node is: 

     IImportNode 
   IExpressionNode <-- getImportNameNode()
    For example, 
    import flash.display.Sprite;
    is represented as 
     IImportNode
   IFullNameNode
     IFullNameNode
       IIdentifierNode "flash"
       IIdentifierNode "display"
     IIdentifierNode "Sprite"
